Package org.mazeApp.model.algorithms

Class AbstractMazeSolver

java.lang.Object
org.mazeApp.model.algorithms.AbstractMazeSolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
MazeSolver
Direct Known Subclasses:
AStarSolver, BFSsolver, DFSsolver, DijkstraSolver, OnlyLeftSolver, OnlyRightSolver, RandomSolver
public abstract class AbstractMazeSolver extends Object implements MazeSolver
Abstract base class providing common functionalities for maze solvers.

This class implements shared logic such as timing execution and storing the resulting path. All concrete solver classes should extend this class.
